---
title: Veggie Dan Dan-Style Noodles with Mushrooms and Spicy Peanut Sauce
description: Creamy peanut and sweet hoisin make a silky sauce for Meatless Farms Veggie Ground and savoury mushrooms! Our unusual take: we've replaced fresh Chinese wheat noodles with quick-cooking spaghetti! Twirl the noodles into the flavourful and "meaty" sauce.
